add working /addTask and /getAllTasks API method + add Pusher notifications
issue.body:
`/addTask` works as needed (saves the task data in DB)
`/getAllTasks` - api method like `/getAllUsers`
`/sendTaskReminders/<taskName>` - put `taskName` there and server will send Pusher notifications on channel `"reminder_channel"`, event name same as user name, and the message contains the `taskName`.
